nter som trenger langvarige behandlinger eller faller ut av arbeidslivet, svarer Ryel.", "(\u00a9NTB)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f964541d505a207cff4e8626e4ba9cf6d6ffcc4d5b7ba146d16704cb1ba8b338"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-03T10:25:50.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "For \u00e5 n\u00e5 m\u00e5let om et r\u00f8ykfritt Norge i 2025 b\u00f8r alle r\u00f8ykesluttprodukter gj\u00f8res gratis, mener Kreftforeningen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/50b710df8c3c938197f96fa99918dfc8604645f4.jpg?5919bbfd"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "R\u00f8ykesluttprodukter b\u00f8r v\u00e6re gratis -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "50b710df8c3c938197f96fa99918dfc8604645f4"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["gj\u00f8res gratis", "r\u00f8yke", "r\u00f8ykesluttprodukter gj\u00f8res", "rene penger", "r\u00f8ykesluttprodukter gj\u00f8res gratis", "milliarder", "r\u00f8ykesluttprodukter", "skriver", "gratis"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["verdens kreftdag", "folkehelseinstituttet", "kreftforeningen", "statens"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["karl e. lund", "anne lise ryel"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value":